, as well as of textual and spiritual concerns, results in a volume of importance to students of religious history and of spirituality. The analysis of the Exercises and the discussion of spiritual direction will also be of great value to ministers and pastors—and to all those pursuing "spiritual life in a secular age."  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aSpiritual exercisesvCongresses. 0aSpiritual exercisesxCongresses. 0aSpiritualityvCongresses. 0aSpiritualityxCatholic ChurchvCongresses. 0aSpiritualityxCatholic ChurchxCongresses. 0aSpiritualityxCongressesxCatholic Church. 4aHistory. 4aReligion: Spirituality. 7aRELIGION / Christianity / Catholic.2bisacsh1 aBuckley, S. J., Michael J., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aClarke, S.J., Thomas E., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCousins, Ewert H., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDupré, Louis, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFahey, S.J., Michael A., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchner, S.J., George P., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aStanley, S. J., David, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package Pre-2010z978311127416408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package pre 2010z978311127724040uhttps://doi.org/10.51644/978088920620540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780889206205423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780889206205/original  a978-3-11-127416-4  ACUP Complete eBook-Package Pre-2010b2010  a978-3-11-127724-0  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package pre 2010b2010  aGBV-deGruyter-alles